Title: May I ask who’s calling, please? A recent rise in VoIP DDoS attacks
Description: Over the past month, multiple Voice over Internet Protocol (VoIP) providers have been targeted by Distributed Denial of Service (DDoS) attacks from entities claiming to be REvil.
